OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers will continue through the
OL,7,Fevening but will clear slowly from the
OL,8,Fsouth overnight. It will become cold
OL,9,Fas clear spells increase later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FDry, early bright spells
OL,12,Feast, otherwise cloudy with rain
OL,13,Fspreading northeast. This heavy at
OL,14,Ftimes and wintry over higher ground.
OL,15,FThe wind strengthens to severe gale
OL,16,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
