OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FRain,
OL,6,Fhill snow and severe gales clear
OL,7,Fovernight into Sunday, leaving
OL,8,Ffrequent showers. Mostly dry but
OL,9,Fcloudy Monday and Tuesday with the
OL,10,Fchance of rain in the west at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
